W

Word - Class in yeezus.memory
A stand-in version of a word (4 bytes) that will be the basis of the memory system in the yeezus OS.
Word() - Constructor for class yeezus.memory.Word
Constructs a new memory.Word with value set to '0x00000000'.
Word(String) - Constructor for class yeezus.memory.Word
Constructs a new memory.Word with the specified value.
Word(long) - Constructor for class yeezus.memory.Word
Constructs a new Word from the specified value.
write(int, Word) - Method in class yeezus.memory.Memory
Writes the given Word to the given physicalAddress.
write(int, Word) - Method in class yeezus.memory.MMU
Writes the given Word to the given physical address.
write(PCB, int, Word) - Method in class yeezus.memory.MMU
Writes the given word to the given logical address for the given process.
